nodes.text: Randar Dowellin was a male crime lord with a unique collection of Galactic Republic artifacts, including a rare Karltonian Fiskin coin. The collection was tagged with a special chemical tracer.
After the collection was stolen by the Bon Seqours, Dowellin sent bounty hunters to track down the collection, which led them to the Farrimmer Cafe on the Mynock 7 Space Station.
